—Yasova Dragonclaw

card.name: Beast Within
card.oracle_text: Destroy target permanent. Its controller creates a 3/3 green Beast creature token.
card.flavor_text:
"Monsters dwell in every heart. We only think civilization tames them."
—Euphemia, Nexus watcher

Boast — {4}{R}: Create a 5/5 red Dragon creature token with flying. (Activate only if this creature attacked this turn and only once each turn.)

card.name: Rapacious Dragon
card.oracle_text:
Flying
When Rapacious Dragon enters, create two Treasure tokens. (They're artifacts with "{T}, Sacrifice this artifact: Add one mana of any color.")
card.flavor_text:
"Surely it won't notice if I take—"
—Theria the Sly, last words

card.name: Draconic Disciple
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add one mana of any color.
{7}, {T}, Sacrifice Draconic Disciple: Create a 5/5 red Dragon creature token with flying.
card.flavor_text: "If I am to die, I will die in the embrace of immeasurable flame."

card.name: Dragonmaster Outcast
card.oracle_text: At the beginning of your upkeep, if you control six or more lands, create a 5/5 red Dragon creature token with flying.
card.flavor_text: "This world will be ruled by its rightful sovereigns, not these hideous pretenders."

card.name: Command Tower
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
card.flavor_text:
"Approach my tower on bended knee or depart from it as ash upon the wind."
—Gadwick, the Wizened

card.name: Talisman of Impulse
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{T}: Add {R} or {G}. Talisman of Impulse deals 1 damage to you.

card.name: Garruk's Uprising
card.oracle_text:
When Garruk's Uprising enters, if you control a creature with power 4 or greater, draw a card.
Creatures you control have trample.
Whenever a creature you control with power 4 or greater enters, draw a card.

card.name: Fires of Yavimaya
card.oracle_text:
Creatures you control have haste.
Sacrifice Fires of Yavimaya: Target creature gets +2/+2 until end of turn.
card.flavor_text: Yavimaya lights the quickest path to battle.

card.name: Commander's Sphere
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
Sacrifice Commander's Sphere: Draw a card.
card.flavor_text: It harmonizes with the essence of its master.

card.name: Path of Ancestry
card.oracle_text:
Path of Ancestry enters tapped.
{T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity. When that mana is spent to cast a creature spell that shares a creature type with your commander, scry 1. (Look at the top card of your library. You may put that card on the bottom.)

card.name: Shamanic Revelation
card.oracle_text:
Draw a card for each creature you control.
Ferocious — You gain 4 life for each creature you control with power 4 or greater.
card.flavor_text: First, whispers of ancient days. Then, visions of things to come.

card.name: Sol Ring
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add {C}{C}.
card.flavor_text: Lost to time is the artificer's art of trapping light from a distant star in a ring of purest gold.

card.name: Akoum Hellkite
card.oracle_text:
Flying
Landfall — Whenever a land you control enters, Akoum Hellkite deals 1 damage to any target. If that land is a Mountain, Akoum Hellkite deals 2 damage instead.

card.name: Arcane Signet
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
card.flavor_text: It started as a mere drop of water. The Magic Mirror crystallized it into much more.

card.name: Atarka Monument
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {R} or {G}.
{4}{R}{G}: Atarka Monument becomes a 4/4 red and green Dragon artifact creature with flying until end of turn.
card.flavor_text: Atarka is worshipped and fed by her subjects at Ayagor, the Dragon's Bowl.

card.name: Blossoming Defense
card.oracle_text: Target creature you control gets +2/+2 and gains hexproof until end of turn.
card.flavor_text: Those who move harmoniously with the flow of aether can channel the power of the natural world.

card.name: Cinder Glade
card.oracle_text:
({T}: Add {R} or {G}.)
Cinder Glade enters tapped unless you control two or more basic lands.
card.flavor_text: On the volcanic continent of Akoum, bizarre vegetation clusters around gas vents, and jagged mountain peaks rise high into the air.

card.name: Chain Reaction
card.oracle_text: Chain Reaction deals X damage to each creature, where X is the number of creatures on the battlefield.
card.flavor_text:
"We train for the improbable, like lightning striking the same place twice, or striking everywhere at once."
—Nundari, Sea Gate militia captain

card.name: Clan Defiance
card.oracle_text:
Choose one or more —
• Clan Defiance deals X damage to target creature with flying.
• Clan Defiance deals X damage to target creature without flying.
• Clan Defiance deals X damage to target player or planeswalker.

card.name: Crucible of Fire
card.oracle_text: Dragon creatures you control get +3/+3.
card.flavor_text:
"The dragon is a perfect marriage of power and the will to use it."
—Sarkhan Vol

card.name: Cultivate
card.oracle_text: Search your library for up to two basic land cards, reveal those cards, put one onto the battlefield tapped and the other into your hand, then shuffle.
card.flavor_text: All seeds share a common bond, calling to each other across infinity.

card.name: Demanding Dragon
card.oracle_text:
Flying
When Demanding Dragon enters, it deals 5 damage to target opponent unless that player sacrifices a creature.
card.flavor_text: A knight's devotion to their steed goes only so far.

card.name: Sakura-Tribe Elder
card.oracle_text: Sacrifice Sakura-Tribe Elder: Search your library for a basic land card, put that card onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
card.flavor_text: He'd chosen a sunlit clearing with open skies and an ample brook. All that remained was to find a worthy sapling.

card.name: Dragonlord's Servant
card.oracle_text: Dragon spells you cast cost {1} less to cast.
card.flavor_text: Atarka serving-goblins coat themselves with grease imbued with noxious herbs, hoping to discourage their ravenous masters from adding them to the meal.

card.name: Return to Nature
card.oracle_text:
Choose one —
• Destroy target artifact.
• Destroy target enchantment.
• Exile target card from a graveyard.
card.flavor_text:
"Even steel and stone return to Ghrin-Danu in time."
—Katilda, Dawnhart Prime

card.name: Dragonspeaker Shaman
card.oracle_text: Dragon spells you cast cost {2} less to cast.
card.flavor_text: "We speak the dragons' language of flame and rage. They speak our language of fury and honor. Together we shall weave a tale of destruction without equal."

card.name: Dragon Tempest
card.oracle_text:
Whenever a creature you control with flying enters, it gains haste until end of turn.
Whenever a Dragon you control enters, it deals X damage to any target, where X is the number of Dragons you control.

card.name: Dragon Mage
card.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever Dragon Mage deals combat damage to a player, each player discards their hand, then draws seven cards.
card.flavor_text: "You'll bend to my will—with or without your precious sanity."

card.name: Dragon's Hoard
card.oracle_text:
Whenever a Dragon you control enters, put a gold counter on Dragon's Hoard.
{T}, Remove a gold counter from Dragon's Hoard: Draw a card.
{T}: Add one mana of any color.

card.name: Dream Pillager
card.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever Dream Pillager deals combat damage to a player, exile that many cards from the top of your library. Until end of turn, you may cast spells from among those exiled cards.
card.flavor_text: Its wings shimmer with dreams absorbed from its enemies.

card.name: Drumhunter
card.oracle_text:
At the beginning of your end step, if you control a creature with power 5 or greater, you may draw a card.
{T}: Add {C}.
card.flavor_text: "I feel the vine-rhythm as my friends drive the beast to me. I will not miss my mark."

card.name: Drakuseth, Maw of Flames
card.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever Drakuseth, Maw of Flames attacks, it deals 4 damage to any target and 3 damage to each of up to two other targets.
card.flavor_text:
"Spread out, you idiots! Spread out!"
—Marsden, party leader, last words

card.name: Elemental Bond
card.oracle_text: Whenever a creature you control with power 3 or greater enters, draw a card.
card.flavor_text:
"I want to help Zendikar. Show me the way."
—Nissa Revane

card.name: Foe-Razer Regent
card.oracle_text:
Flying
When Foe-Razer Regent enters, you may have it fight target creature you don't control.
Whenever a creature you control fights, put two +1/+1 counters on it at the beginning of the next end step.

card.name: Flameblast Dragon
card.oracle_text:
Flying
Whenever Flameblast Dragon attacks, you may pay {X}{R}. If you do, Flameblast Dragon deals X damage to any target.

card.name: Furnace Whelp
card.oracle_text:
Flying
{R}: Furnace Whelp gets +1/+0 until end of turn.
card.flavor_text: Baby dragons can't figure out humans—if they didn't want to be killed, why were they made of meat and treasure?

card.name: Game Trail

As Game Trail enters, you may reveal a Mountain or Forest card from your hand. If you don't, Game Trail enters tapped.
{T}: Add {R} or {G}.

As Frontier Siege enters, choose Khans or Dragons.
• Khans — At the beginning of each of your main phases, add {G}{G}.
• Dragons — Whenever a creature with flying enters under your control, you may have it fight target creature you don't control.

card.name: Harmonize
card.oracle_text: Draw three cards.
card.flavor_text:
"Animals commune with their environment without the need for language. Theirs is a fundamental connection that surpasses flimsy words."
—Vivien Reid

card.name: Harbinger of the Hunt

Flying

{2}{G}: Harbinger of the Hunt deals 1 damage to each other creature with flying.

Flying
{3}{R}: Destroy target artifact. Hoard-Smelter Dragon gets +X/+0 until end of turn, where X is that artifact's mana value.

"The predator knows the true way of the world. Life is conflict. Only the strong survive."
—Garruk Wildspeaker
